                    <div class="step-block">
                        <span class="step-label say">Say</span>
                        <div class="talk-track">
                            <p>Benton, you asked about performance metrics &mdash; handle time, wait time,
                                call duration. All of that is captured natively here because the phone, email,
                                and chat all run through one platform. You don&rsquo;t need to pull a report from
                                Genesys for talk time, a separate report from Salesforce for case metrics, and then
                                reconcile them in Excel. One system, one source of truth for every metric.</p>
                        </div>
